:30435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]檸檬8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識食呀檸檬8，日本winton出左隻綠色盒好似蜜瓜味幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出咗成年啦！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyT32DG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyT32DG.jpg&h=5d6a1713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小清新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正呀呢隻！蜜瓜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想買一條 可惜機場無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987b75f99e00b842f6b33c1b97aa57e7058c143f","tid":130311,"uid":30435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/234041_8a3ad0946aaf8a07f7edd786c2e13c33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F234041_8a3ad0946aaf8a07f7edd786c2e13c33.jpg&h=223a276d&s={SIZE}\" />呢隻個盒好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜又係無咩味...仲要係一..試過就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc27a8da4be014d7799aac93a35f9faf71bc2ee","tid":130311,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"藍莓點會無人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一出食到而家取代咗黑冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆就食緊1仔，由健1轉黑1再轉萬事發，好似叫晶白？不過佢有時都拎我啲煙食，有時買咗啲新味唔啱食都係俾佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早幾個月見到日本街機有西瓜味，買咗包試大家都話中咗伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid